{"tid":650092,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港既大學入學考試愈改愈淺，只會令大陸學生得益！","createTime":"2018-05-02T04:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T15:40:10.000Z","uid":14170,"like":64,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0e534c475d25d27f86f7c1cc080928291e660de6","tid":650092,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"本來 Jupas 入到大學既香港學生，底子唔夠已經比大陸學生屈機，依家大陸學生既 GPA 係由 3.5 起跳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩佢地目標係去美國 Master，唔係留係香港搵工，暫時本土學生畢到業，GPA 過三都有好多工請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家連 DSE 都有大陸人考 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢慢本土學生會被比下去，未入大學前已經輸左，連大學學位都輸埋就乜鳩都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e0df43973564dec14fcacd6abe5b78c09cb6ae","tid":650092,"uid":84212,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbd1bcf4a2a1a8c43e6dac7e420214570aeab6cc","tid":650092,"uid":179967,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"有撚計咩<br />\n爭氣先得架"},{"pid":"db6d9132c4c9752dfb030a4c609a6f345d3d083b","tid":650092,"uid":180404,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"成個大陸gum Q多人<br />\n就gum睇牌面都已經知香港比人禁住黎打<br />\n<br />\n你以為佢地去左美國讀Master成件事就完..太天真了<br />\n到你想讀Master又係要對抽多次<br />\n佢地去美國名牌大學讀完master之後，有唔少會黎香港做野<br />\n<br />\n假以時日，等佢地做到上高職, d local面對ge情況仲嚴峻tbh<br />\n<br />\n利申: 已經面對緊以上情況"},{"pid":"f88c0954e11c10731c28914f3103b2e8f1c6190b","tid":650092,"uid":43523,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"人口比例問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸人口多過我地成200倍，就算喺入面每10000個人搵1個精英都有130000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 裡面有一成人走過嚟讀書都死"},{"pid":"da9ac17a66e3327c3aba864dc70a20c041796ce4","tid":650092,